                            <pb facs="0866" n="780" xml:id="pg_780"/>
                            <p>8. The effect of meeting the Russian Protocol on the movement of U.
                                S. troops overseas and maintaining them thereafter would be on the
                                following order:</p>
                            <p rend="center"><hi rend="smallcaps">table iv</hi></p>
                            <table cols="2" rend="width: 60%" rendition="#center-block" rows="6">
                                <row>
                                    <cell>
                                        <hi rend="italic">1943</hi>
                                    </cell>
                                    <cell role="num">
                                        <hi rend="italic">No. of troops</hi>
                                    </cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell>1st Quarter</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">46,000</cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
